description:
Big.Freedia.S02.WS.DSR.x264-NY2


Big Freedia, a gospel prodigy turned larger-than-life Bounce star, is on a mission to take New Orleans' Bounce music from the clubs of Canal Street to the top of the charts and the great arenas of the world.


Can Freedia stay true to her roots as her stardom rises? Can she keep her New Orleans friends and family together as she moves onto the national stage? And is the world ready for the drop-dead dazzling, gender-bending "Queen Diva of Bounce", Big Freedia? 



Included here are all 8 episodes of Season 2
